{"tid":951332,"cid":19,"subCid":0,"title":"都唔知成績唔好嘅人諗乜 心態超奇怪","createTime":"2018-12-22T09:02:04.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-22T10:39:02.000Z","uid":73094,"like":31,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"881edf900ecb2bcb7adb0903695e290a95ab676e","tid":951332,"uid":73094,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-22T09:02:04.000Z","msg":"讀緊HD 發覺無乜真心fd<br />\n真心對人 人地利用完你就掰鳩掰<br />\n一係有嘢唔識 佢地想有人carry先靠近自己咁<br />\n我問返佢地嘢 一係藍剔一係無視<br />\n平時就搭哂膊頭 懶係fd咁<br />\n一sem break 就斷哂聯絡 <br />\n仲要特登開個小圈子（另一個班gp) wts gp 但無加我<br />\n成班都係成績比較差果類 成績好嘅一個都無加<br />\n人以群分？成績好剩係得比人利用嘅價值？<br />\n<br />\n仲有佢地平時好勤力 但出成績 低分<br />\n又話無溫過書 <br />\n但次次見我高分過佢地 就燒埋我果疊 話唔會似我咁努力喎<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/clown2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n唉 遲吓返工 世途仲險惡 好難識真心朋友<br />\n成日都勁無安全感<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"29ce787f6800ab19ba15d9a24f718e1108d70edb","tid":951332,"uid":192491,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-22T09:02:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b6a9703b080f79bded66560036539245bc4a7435","tid":951332,"uid":206222,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-22T09:03:39.000Z","msg":"Agree"},{"pid":"1d972dda0fe5d5b092a4a4118c7ca0f0bd23ddf9","tid":951332,"uid":154212,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-22T09:04:45.000Z","msg":"出到黎係咁架啦<br />\n你無利用價值，理你做咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9f3e2ee2956e78309b1a580cf77defd8404d96a0","tid":951332,"uid":73094,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"1d972dda0fe5d5b092a4a4118c7ca0f0bd23ddf9","tid":951332,"uid":154212,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-22T09:04:45.000Z","msg":"出到黎係咁架啦<br />\n你無利用價值，理你做咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-22T09:08:43.000Z","msg":"咁即係大家都咁廢 先做到有傾有笑 私下會聯絡嘅fd?<img src=\"/